s="icon-arrow alk-icon-derecha"></i></div></div></li><li class="js-open-modal-PDP-components" data-id="store-availability"><div class="menu_desktop_item"><div class="new-container__main-product__pdp-features__pdp_buttons-aditional-features-wrapper-text-icon"><div class="new-container__main-product__pdp-features__pdp_buttons-aditional-features-wrapper-icon"><div><i class="alk-icon-nuestras-tiendas"></i></div></div><div class="new-container__main-product__pdp-features__pdp_buttons-aditional-features-wrapper-text"><p>Consultar disponibilidad en tiendas</p></div></div><div class="new-container__main-product__pdp-features__pdp_buttons-aditional-features-wrapper-arrow"><i class="icon-arrow alk-icon-derecha"></i></div></div><div class="menu_mobile_item"><div class="menu_mobile_item_wrapper"><div class="menu_mobile_item_icon"><i class="alk-icon-nuestras-tiendas"></i></div><div class="menu_mobile_item_text"><p>Consultar disponibilidad en tiendas</p></div></div><div class="menu_mobile_item_arrow"><i class="icon-arrow alk-icon-derecha"></i></div></div></li><li class="js-open-modal-PDP-components" data-id="modalExtendedWarranty"><div class="menu_desktop_item"><div class="new-container__main-product__pdp-features__pdp_buttons-aditional-features-wrapper-text-icon"><div class="new-container__main-product__pdp-features__pdp_buttons-aditional-features-wrapper-icon"><div><i class="alk-icon-garantia"></i></div></div><div class="new-container__main-product__pdp-features__pdp_buttons-aditional-features-wrapper-text"><p>Extiende la garant&iacute;a y protege tu producto contra da&ntilde;o accidental</p></div></div><div class="new-container__main-product__pdp-features__pdp_buttons-aditional-features-wrapper-arrow"><i class="icon-arrow alk-icon-derecha"></i></div></div><div class="menu_mobile_item"><div class="menu_mobile_item_wrapper"><div class="menu_mobile_item_icon"><i class="alk-icon-garantia"></i></div><div class="menu_mobile_item_text"><p>Extiende la garant&iacute;a y protege tu producto contra da&ntilde;o accidental</p></div></div><div class="menu_mobile_item_arrow"><i class="icon-arrow alk-icon-derecha"></i></div></div></li></ul></div></div><div class="new-container__about loading"><div class="new-container__about__container"><div class="new-container__titles"><h2 class="js-subtitle-pdp"> Características destacadas</h2></div><ul class="tab-details__keyFeatures--list"><li class="tab-details__keyFeatures--item">Micrófono direccional de 3 cápsulas y paravientos</li><li class="tab-details__keyFeatures--item">Desenfoca el fondo fácilmente y agrega un efecto bokeh</li><li class="tab-details__keyFeatures--item">Potente estabilización de imagen</li></ul></div><div class="new-container__about__container"><div class="new-container__titles"><h2 class="js-subtitle-pdp new-container__titles"> Resumen del producto</h2></div><div class="tab-details__description"><alk-rich-content template="wc-product-characteristics"></alk-rich-content><template id="wc-product-characteristics"> La cámara ZV-1 en color negro, es la herramienta ideal para la creación de contenidos audiovisuales, gracias a funciones inteligentes que ayudan a tener videos de alta calidad, su sistema de audio permite grabar incluso en exteriores con un sonido claro, su pantalla multi ángulo permite ajustarse a diferentes tipos de grabación y su combinación de Sensor de imagen 1 pulgada y lente Carl Zeiss logran un detalle excepcional en las grabaciones de contenidos ¡Adquiere la tuya aquí!</template></div><div class="more_characteristics" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#modalDetailDescription"><span>Ver la descripción detallada</span><i class="alk-icon-derecha"></i></div></div><div class="bg-full-width"></div></div></div><a class="addCartFloat js-addCartFloat" hidden="hidden" id="addCartButtonFloat">Agregar al carrito</a></div><div class="js-sticky_header js-sticky_header_movable sticky_header_movable sticky_header "><div class="new-container max-width-container sticky_header-wrapper loading"><ul class="js-list-anchor"></ul><div class="sticky_header_info"><div class="sticky_header_info_price"><div class="js-sticky_header_price_discount sticky_header_info_price_discount "></div><div class="js-sticky_header_price_normal sticky_header_info_price_normal"></div></div><div class="sticky_header_info_btn"><button id="simulate-click-add" class="button-primary js-simulate-click-add">Agregar al carrito</button></div></div></div></div><div class="js-sticky_header js-sticky_header_static sticky_header_static sticky_header "><div class="new-container max-width-container sticky_header-wrapper loading"><ul class="js-list-anchor"></ul><div class="sticky_header_info"><div class="sticky_header_info_price"><div class="js-sticky_header_price_discount sticky_header_info_price_discount "></div><div class="js-sticky_header_price_normal sticky_header_info_price_normal"></div></div><div class="sticky_header_info_btn"><button id="simulate-click-add" class="button-primary js-simulate-click-add">Agregar al carrito</button></div></div></div></div><div class="new-container max-width-container"><div class="new-container--background--gray--mobile"><div class="new-container__container js-product-container new-container__description js-product-container-description desktop loading"><div class="new-container__titles alkosto-title"><h2 class="js-subtitle-pdp"> Descripción del producto</h2></div><alk-rich-content template="wc-product-description"></alk-rich-content><template id="wc-product-description"><style>
	.container-2 {
		width: 100%;
		max-width: 1366px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0;
	}

	/* sección 01 */

	.section-enrichment-one {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: row;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1em;
		padding: 2em 4em;
		margin-bottom: 4em;
	}

	.bg-gray {
		background-color: #F5F5F5;
	}

	.section-enrichment-one .hero-text {
		width: 40%;
	}

	.hero-text h1 span:first-child {
		display: block;
		font-size: 50px;
	}

	.hero-text h1 {
		font-size: 72px;
		line-height: 78px;
	}

	.hero-text p {
		width: 100%;
	}

	.section-enrichment-one img {
		width: 36%;
	}

	/* sección 02 */

	.section-enrichment-two {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: row;
		justify-content: space-between;
		gap: 1em;
		padding: 4em;
		border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e070;
	}

	.section-enrichment-two .two-image {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: row;
		gap: 4em;
		width: 50%;
	}

	.section-enrichment-two .two-image img:nth-child(1) {
		align-self: flex-start;
		margin-top: -4em;
	}

	.section-enrichment-two .two-image img:nth-child(2) {
		align-self: flex-end;
	}

	.section-enrichment-two .features-text {
		width: 50%;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 4em;
	}

	.features-text h2 {
		font-size: 48px;
		line-height: 52px;
		align-self: flex-end;
		width: 80%;
		text-align: end;
	}

	.features-text p {
		text-align: right;
	}

	/* sección 03 */
	.section-enrichment-three {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: row;
		justify-content: space-between;
		padding: 4em 4em 2em;
	}

	.section-enrichment-three .feature {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: flex-start;
		width: calc(33% - 5em);
	}


	.section-enrichment-three .feature h3 {
		font-size: 18px;
		color: #707070;
	}

	.section-enrichment-three .feature p {
		font-size: 14px;
		color: #707070;
		text-align: left;
	}

	/* sección 04 */

	.section-enrichment-four {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: row;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 4em;
		padding: 2em 4em 0;
		border-radius: 16px;
		margin-bottom: 2em;
	}

	.section-enrichment-four .img-text {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		width: 50%;
	}

	.img-text h3 {
		text-align: left;
	}

	.section-enrichment-four .img-text span {
		display: block;
		font-size: 40px;
	}

	.section-enrichment-four .chars {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		width: 50%;
		border-left: 1px solid#e0e0e070;
		padding-left: 4em;
	}

	.section-enrichment-four .chars .card {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: row;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: center;
		padding-bottom: 2em;
		border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e070;
	}

	.section-enrichment-four .chars .card:last-child {
		border-bottom: none;
	}

	.chars .card h3 {
		font-size: 18px;
		text-align: left;
	}

	.chars .card p {
		font-size: 14px;
		color: var(--text-color1);
		margin: 0;
		text-align: left;
	}


	.icon-color-one {
		background-color: #FFA77A;
		border-radius: 8px;
		padding: .1em;
	}

	.icon-color-two {
		background-color: #B7C5FF;
		border-radius: 8px;
		padding: .1em;
	}

	.icon-color-three {
		background-color: darkgray;
		border-radius: 8px;
		padding: .1em;
	}

	.section-enrichment-four iframe {
		width: 100%
	}


	/* RESPONSIVE */

	@media only screen and (max-width:1200px) {
		.section-enrichment-two .two-image {
			width: auto;
		}

		.section-enrichment-two .features-text {
			width: auto;
		}
	}

	@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {

		.section-enrichment-one .hero-text {
			width: 50%;
		}

		.hero-text h1 span:first-child {
			font-size: 30px;
		}

		.hero-text h1 {
			font-size: 50px;
			line-height: 52px;
		}

		.section-enrichment-two .two-image {
			gap: 2em;
		}

		.section-enrichment-two .features-text {
			gap: 2em;
		}

		.features-text h2 {
			font-size: 32px;
			line-height: 36px;
		}

		.section-enrichment-three .feature {
			width: calc(36% - 5em);
		}

		.section-enrichment-three .feature img {
			width: 100%;
		}


		.section-enrichment-four {
			gap: 2em;
		}

		#modalDetailDescription .modal-content .modal-body,
		#modalOpinions .modal-content .modal-body,
		#modalTableSpecs .modal-content .modal-body,
		#store-availability .modal-content .modal-body {
			padding-bottom: 20vh !important;
		}

	}

	@media only screen and (max-width:820px) {
		.section-enrichment-two {
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: center;
		}

		.features-text h2 {
			align-self: center;
		}

		.features-text p {
			text-align: center;
		}


		.section-enrichment-four .img-text {
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
			width: 100%;
		}

		.section-enrichment-four {
			flex-direction: column;
			justify-content: center;
			align-items: center;
		}

		.section-enrichment-four .chars {
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: row;
			justify-content: space-between;
			width: 100%;
			border-left: none;
			padding-left: 0;
		}

		.section-enrichment-four .chars .card {
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column-reverse;
			justify-content: flex-start;
			align-items: center;
			padding-bottom: 0;
			border-bottom: none;
		}

		.chars .card h3 {
			font-size: 16px;
			text-align: center;
		}

		.chars .card p {
			font-size: 12px;
			text-align: center;
		}
	}

	@media only screen and (max-width:767px) {
		.section-enrichment-one {
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column-reverse;
			position: relative;
		}

		.section-enrichment-one .hero-text {
			width: 100%;
			text-align: center;
		}

		.hero-text h1 {
			position: absolute;
			top: 1em;
			left: 50%;
			transform: translateX(-50%);
			font-size: 39px;
			line-height: 44px;
		}

		.img-text h3 {
			text-align: center;
		}

		.section-enrichment-four .img-text {
			width: 100%;
		}

		.section-enrichment-one img {
			width: 100%;
			margin-top: 8em;
		}

		.section-enrichment-two {
			position: relative;
		}

		.features-text h2 {
			position: absolute;
			top: 0;
			left: 50%;
			transform: translateX(-50%);
			text-align: center;
		}

		.section-enrichment-two .two-image {
			margin-top: 7em;
		}

		.section-enrichment-four iframe {
			width: 100%;
			height: 240px;
		}
	}

	@media only screen and (max-width:680px) {

		.container-2 {
			padding: 0;
		}
		


